articles.title: White: Winner of Aspinall vs Pavlovich shelved until Jones fights Miocic in 2024 — ‘They’re gonna have to wai… - MMA Mania
articles.description: UFC CEO Dana White will make the winner of Tom Aspinall vs. Sergei Pavlovich, who collide at UFC 295 for the interim heavyweight title, wait for the winner of Jon Jones vs. Stipe Miocic in 2024.
articles.content: UFC fans may not see a heavyweight title unification bout until late 2024 or even early 2025.
